articles.title: Calm pervades Niger's capital as deadline to reverse coup expires - Reuters
articles.description: Niger's capital was calm on Sunday, with citizens appearing undaunted by the threat of military intervention by West Africa's regional bloc, as its ultimatum for the country's coup leaders to reinstate the president expires.
